<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.ibm.com/news/us/en/2008/06/2008_06_09.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ibm.com/news/us/en/2008/06/2008_06_09.html" rel="nofollow">"Los Alamos computer breaks petaflop barrier"</a>. IBM. 2008-06-09<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.ibm.com/news/us/en/2008/06/2008_06_09.html" class="external free" title="http://www.ibm.com/news/us/en/2008/06/2008_06_09.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.ibm.com/news/us/en/2008/06/2008_06_09.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-06-12</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Los+Alamos+computer+breaks+petaflop+barrier&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2008-06-09&amp;rft.pub=IBM&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibm.com%2Fnews%2Fus%2Fen%2F2008%2F06%2F2008_06_09.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:IBM_Roadrunner"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFKevin_J._Barker.2C_Kei_Davis.2C_Adolfy_Hoisie.2C_Darren_J._Kerbyson.2C_Mike_Lang.2C_Scott_Pakin.2C_Jose_C._Sancho">Kevin J. Barker, Kei Davis, Adolfy Hoisie, Darren J. Kerbyson, Mike Lang, Scott Pakin, Jose C. Sancho. <a href="http://www.c3.lanl.gov/~kei/mypubbib/papers/SC08:Roadrunner.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.c3.lanl.gov/~kei/mypubbib/papers/SC08:Roadrunner.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Entering the Petaflop Era: The Architecture and Performance of Roadrunner"</a> (PDF)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.c3.lanl.gov/~kei/mypubbib/papers/SC08:Roadrunner.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.c3.lanl.gov/~kei/mypubbib/papers/SC08:Roadrunner.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.c3.lanl.gov/~kei/mypubbib/papers/SC08:Roadrunner.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-11-22</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Entering+the+Petaflop+Era%3A+The+Architecture+and+Performance+of+Roadrunner&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Kevin+J.+Barker%2C+Kei+Davis%2C+Adolfy+Hoisie%2C+Darren+J.+Kerbyson%2C+Mike+Lang%2C+Scott+Pakin%2C+Jose+C.+Sancho&amp;rft.au=Kevin+J.+Barker%2C+Kei+Davis%2C+Adolfy+Hoisie%2C+Darren+J.+Kerbyson%2C+Mike+Lang%2C+Scott+Pakin%2C+Jose+C.+Sancho&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.c3.lanl.gov%2F%7Ekei%2Fmypubbib%2Fpapers%2FSC08%3ARoadrunner.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:IBM_Roadrunner"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
